## ğŸ§© 4. Conversion Planning

- [ ] Create a plan to handle each format specifier:
  - `%c` â†’ character
  - `%s` â†’ string
  - `%p` â†’ pointer
  - `%d` / `%i` â†’ integers
  - `%u` â†’ unsigned integer
  - `%x` / `%X` â†’ hexadecimal
  - `%%` â†’ percent sign

- [ ] Plan internal helper functions for each type.
